Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,柚子 我對不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:43.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等 從陽台那裡就能和往常一樣出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:45.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,陽台？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,春香 真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:52.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,哦呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:55.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,咦誒誒~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有飛過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我先走一步
